      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always kept it tucked away in the garage and hand-washed it every single weekend. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved by a true car person, you\u2019ve found it. Come on over, let's chat cars, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
