    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the S65-powered E92, a masterclass in high-revving atmospheric induction. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity and optimal thermal cycles. Recent preventative overhaul includes VAC coated rod bearings and updated throttle actuators to ensure the 8,400 RPM redline remains a reliable playground. The DCT logic has been flashed for crisper engagement, perfectly complementing the EDC-tuned suspension geometry. No deferred maintenance; the subframe is reinforced, and the VANOS system shows zero deviation in timing. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a zero-compromise precision instrument for the discerning driver who values peak volumetric efficiency and structural integrity.",
